name: Mr Hoots tote bag (HPB0313)
description:
Mr Hoots is an original illustration by herphotoblog

This canvas tote is made from 100% post-industrial recycled cotton, making it environmentally and socially responsible. The bag measures 13.5" x 15.5" with 5.5" side & bottom gussets and 23" x 1.5" cotton web shoulder straps, which allow you to comfortably carry the bag either over the shoulder or as a tote. All seams and stress points are double stitched for durability, plus there's a pocket inside measuring 5.5" x 6".
